<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . / Nü iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_122_r2l18">der <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan></del>
<expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Jude für vns komen vnd hat vns fürgetragen
